INSERT OR REPLACE INTO "texts" VALUES ("100217022","Amazoness Pet Liger","""Amazoness Tiger"" + 1 ""Amazoness"" monster
If this card attacks, during damage calculation: You can make this card gain 500 ATK during that damage calculation only. If an ""Amazoness"" monster you control attacks an opponent's monster, after damage calculation: You can target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; it loses 800 ATK. Monsters your opponent controls cannot attack face-up ""Amazoness"" monsters, except this one.","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","");
